sections.heading: of Economic Development; furnish advice and information
sections.text: The Department of Economic Development shall furnish advice and information in connection with a project when requested to do so by a county or municipality.SourceLaws 1961, c. 54, § 10, p. 207;Laws 1969, c. 104, § 1, p. 479;R.S.1943, (1983), §

13-1110.Department of Economic Development; furnish advice and information.

The Department of Economic Development shall furnish advice and information in connection with a project when requested to do so by a county or municipality.

SourceLaws 1961, c. 54, § 10, p. 207;Laws 1969, c. 104, § 1, p. 479;R.S.1943, (1983), § 18-1623.
